{"tid":124140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七警判監】庭外反應兩極　說普通話撐警女子激動嚎哭　黃傘市民歡呼慶祝","createTime":"2017-02-17T11:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T11:05:53.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"472a7538571195d13a3703d7d4581589601191f6","tid":124140,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:02:48.000Z","msg":"【七警判監】庭外反應兩極　說普通話撐警女子激動嚎哭　黃傘市民歡呼慶祝<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/七警判監-庭外反應兩極-說普通話撐警女子激動嚎哭-黃傘市民歡呼慶祝/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3-%E5%BA%AD%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E5%85%A9%E6%A5%B5-%E8%AA%AA%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%BF%80%E5%8B%95%E5%9A%8E%E5%93%AD-%E9%BB%83%E5%82%98%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%AD%A1%E5%91%BC%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%2F&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=031458ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3-%E5%BA%AD%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E5%85%A9%E6%A5%B5-%E8%AA%AA%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%BF%80%E5%8B%95%E5%9A%8E%E5%93%AD-%E9%BB%83%E5%82%98%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%AD%A1%E5%91%BC%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%2F&h=ec3e0cd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/七警判監-庭外反應兩極-說普通話撐警女子激動嚎哭-黃傘市民歡呼慶祝/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/reaction-10_aw3To_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Freaction-10_aw3To_1200x0.png&h=93c74472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法庭今早宣布「七警案」判刑，七名被告全部判監兩年，不可緩刑。公眾聞判反應兩極，有女子在法庭外激動嚎哭，大嘆判刑對警察不公。場外有舉黃傘的市民得悉判決後歡呼慶祝，欲噴派對彩帶時被警員制止。<br />\n<br />\n法庭今早約十時宣布七警全部判監兩年，有旁聽公眾即場大叫「好嘢！」散庭後更有人大叫「抵你個仔坐監」，有一名短髮女子激動回應：「收聲啦！」惟當記者問及其身份時，對方則不肯透露。"},{"pid":"c6160a78a9d2841bc85ce4ffc700a4d5df02b264","tid":124140,"uid":15356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e525b4e6c89280577b9cb0019aeee0918820b8","tid":124140,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/16797887_10154854850961422_8961768503696663586_o-1_Iiui6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F16797887_10154854850961422_8961768503696663586_o-1_Iiui6_1200x0.png&h=3fe5bc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說普通話女子大哭　居港已六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另有一名女子在庭外嚎啕大哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，哭聲十分淒厲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，需被送到證人室休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。她冷靜過後離開，記者問及她大哭的原因，操普通話的她表示自己並非七名被告的家人，來港定居已六年，指「（判刑）對警察很不公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」認為是判重了，「警察很難做」，而她不認為曾健超被襲是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/16640845_10154154764701105_864246455173725390_n_7FGQ1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F16640845_10154154764701105_864246455173725390_n_7FGQ1_1200x0.png&h=e142ecb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名女子在庭外嚎啕大哭<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，法院外公眾反應同樣兩極。有舉黃傘的市民得悉判決後歡呼慶祝，欲噴派對彩帶時被警員制止。「香港政研會」、正義聯盟黨等撐警組織，則打算明天遊行，表達對「七警案」判決的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police-05_qFLJD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice-05_qFLJD_1200x0.png&h=03c2b217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「香港政研會」主席鄧德成在法庭外向傳媒表示，已有二百名市民報名出席遊行，明午三點由遮打花園遊行至政府總部，途中會到警總向警員獻上心意咭。鄧德成說，遊行目的要讓司法界知道，市民對司法不公極不滿意。他指對判決感極度失望，法官無保留地接受疲弱的證據，證人的品德又有問題，而判刑較「佔中暴徒」重得多，「一邊從寛一邊從嚴」，刑容七警行為是執法上的瑕疵，令人不能理解。"}]}